OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey and potentially murky
OL,6,Fstart, however cloud will gradually
OL,7,Fthin and break up allowing skies to
OL,8,Fbrighten. Some sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, especially in
OL,10,Fthe southeast. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fprolonged sunny spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry night to come with
OL,14,Fclear skies in the southeast and some
OL,15,Fpatchy cloud in the west and north.
OL,16,FMild for most places and can feel
OL,17,Fmuggy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
