OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny cloud in the west and
OL,6,Fnorth will lift and break through the
OL,7,Fmorning, bringing bright and sunny
OL,8,Fspells for most places. Feeling very
OL,9,Fwarm in the sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,12,Fmore settled into the weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure starts to build from the
OL,14,Fsouth. Sunny spells and feeling very
OL,15,Fwarm with temperatures well above the
OL,16,FJune average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
